1
00:00:35,479 --> 00:00:36,520
It's here. There's a hole.

2
00:00:36,799 --> 00:00:37,439
We overlooked it just now.

3
00:00:37,439 --> 00:00:37,920
Fatty.

4
00:00:38,240 --> 00:00:38,759
Come here.

5
00:00:38,759 --> 00:00:39,240
Come on.

6
00:00:39,719 --> 00:00:40,200
Come on.

7
00:00:49,399 --> 00:00:50,200
Coming.

8
00:00:50,280 --> 00:00:51,079
It won't open.

9
00:00:54,560 --> 00:00:55,960
Hurry up!

10
00:00:58,439 --> 00:00:59,159
Hurry up!

11
00:00:59,159 --> 00:01:01,640
Coming, coming, coming!

12
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:10,920
Hurry up!

13
00:01:11,799 --> 00:01:13,920
Together. One, two, three!

14
00:01:19,040 --> 00:01:19,480
Hurry up!

15
00:01:19,480 --> 00:01:20,359
Hurry up and go! Go!

16
00:01:22,239 --> 00:01:23,519
Hurry!

17
00:01:26,879 --> 00:01:28,319
Hurry up! They're coming!

18
00:01:31,719 --> 00:01:32,799
They won't keep chasing us, right?

19
00:01:33,760 --> 00:01:34,439
No, they won't.

20
00:01:34,680 --> 00:01:35,319
That's great.

21
00:01:35,439 --> 00:01:36,480
That's impossible.

22
00:01:51,640 --> 00:01:52,079
Are you okay?

23
00:01:52,079 --> 00:01:53,120
Wh-What's going on?

24
00:01:54,879 --> 00:01:55,599
Martial Uncle.

25
00:01:55,640 --> 00:01:56,840
All along our way here,

26
00:01:57,400 --> 00:01:58,799
it's been nothing but spikes and thorns.

27
00:01:58,920 --> 00:01:59,879
Could you figure out

28
00:01:59,920 --> 00:02:01,319
if there are any traps?

29
00:02:01,599 --> 00:02:02,640
Let's be careful.

30
00:02:03,200 --> 00:02:04,400
Watch your step.

31
00:02:04,719 --> 00:02:06,719
Make sure not to touch anything

32
00:02:06,799 --> 00:02:08,520
to avoid triggering any traps.

33
00:02:34,039 --> 00:02:35,120
Professor Lu, watch out!

34
00:02:35,199 --> 00:02:35,840
Who is it?

35
00:02:36,479 --> 00:02:37,240
Professor Lu, it's me.

36
00:02:37,240 --> 00:02:38,080
Who? You?

37
00:02:38,479 --> 00:02:40,039
D-Don't point that at me.

38
00:02:40,039 --> 00:02:41,439
I didn't touch anything.

39
00:02:41,719 --> 00:02:42,919
Right, right. I can testify.

40
00:02:42,919 --> 00:02:44,439
Old Lu didn't touch anything this time.

41
00:02:45,879 --> 00:02:46,960
Someone must be controlling it.

42
00:02:48,479 --> 00:02:49,280
Watch me.

43
00:03:20,199 --> 00:03:20,919
Come out!

44
00:03:21,919 --> 00:03:22,759
Martial Uncle. Come out!

45
00:03:23,560 --> 00:03:24,360
Sorry to bother you,

46
00:03:25,039 --> 00:03:26,159
b-but you should look over there.

47
00:03:39,319 --> 00:03:40,919
This Missy is an old acquaintance.

48
00:03:41,759 --> 00:03:42,919
Nobody make a move.

49
00:03:43,439 --> 00:03:44,960
I'll go talk to this Missy.

50
00:03:46,280 --> 00:03:46,759
Missy.

51
00:03:47,360 --> 00:03:48,080
Well...

52
00:03:48,520 --> 00:03:49,240
Missy.

53
00:03:49,520 --> 00:03:50,719
As the saying goes,

54
00:03:51,080 --> 00:03:53,159
strangers at first, friends at second.

55
00:03:53,560 --> 00:03:55,159
We're practically acquaintances now.

56
00:03:55,479 --> 00:03:57,639
We are all good people.

57
00:03:58,280 --> 00:03:59,199
We're not here to cause trouble.

58
00:03:59,199 --> 00:03:59,960
You know?

59
00:03:59,960 --> 00:04:01,120
I also have to tell you...

60
00:04:02,639 --> 00:04:04,719
Can she even understand you blabbering?

61
00:04:05,479 --> 00:04:06,919
Whether she understands or not,

62
00:04:07,000 --> 00:04:08,599
we'll know once I say it.

63
00:04:09,120 --> 00:04:10,039
In case she does understand,

64
00:04:10,039 --> 00:04:11,360
the misunderstanding between us...

65
00:04:11,360 --> 00:04:12,280
There is no misunderstanding.

66
00:04:14,240 --> 00:04:15,719
It's you who won't give up your thieving ways.

67
00:04:16,759 --> 00:04:17,560
She understood.

68
00:04:17,839 --> 00:04:18,639
Lady Warrior.

69
00:04:18,959 --> 00:04:19,920
Calm down, Lady Warrior.

70
00:04:20,079 --> 00:04:21,040
We just

71
00:04:21,240 --> 00:04:23,519
plan to pass through here, that's all.

72
00:04:23,759 --> 00:04:24,920
We are all good people.

73
00:04:25,079 --> 00:04:26,920
You come to my territory to run wild,

74
00:04:27,040 --> 00:04:28,319
what kind of good people are you?

75
00:04:28,319 --> 00:04:30,040
We are all archaeologists.

76
00:04:30,240 --> 00:04:32,439
We absolutely have no intention of destroying anything.

77
00:04:33,040 --> 00:04:35,319
Earlier, I just wanted to drive you out.

78
00:04:35,879 --> 00:04:37,319
Since you refuse to learn,

79
00:04:38,040 --> 00:04:39,199
then death is your only option.

80
00:04:40,120 --> 00:04:41,000
So you're saying,

81
00:04:41,199 --> 00:04:43,519
those villagers from before

82
00:04:43,639 --> 00:04:45,120
were also arranged by you, right?

83
00:04:45,240 --> 00:04:47,240
All the obstacles you've faced here

84
00:04:47,720 --> 00:04:49,120
were arranged by me.

85
00:04:49,319 --> 00:04:50,279
Then those

86
00:04:50,279 --> 00:04:52,240
snakes, bugs, and rats we met were your doing too?

87
00:04:52,519 --> 00:04:53,199
That's right.

88
00:04:53,199 --> 00:04:54,560
I've fought with them before.

89
00:04:54,839 --> 00:04:57,120
Among those who ambushed you,

90
00:04:57,399 --> 00:04:59,439
someone must be controlling living creatures.

91
00:05:00,959 --> 00:05:01,920
Let me tell you,

92
00:05:02,399 --> 00:05:04,120
your Fat Master's biggest fear in life,

93
00:05:06,160 --> 00:05:07,800
his biggest hatred, is snakes, bugs, and rats.

94
00:05:08,279 --> 00:05:09,040
Missy,

95
00:05:09,160 --> 00:05:11,560
doing this is really unrighteous of you.

96
00:05:12,600 --> 00:05:14,600
If you have an issue, let's settle it openly.

97
00:05:14,600 --> 00:05:15,639
What's the point of playing dirty?

98
00:05:15,639 --> 00:05:16,839
Fat Master has thrown his gun away too.

99
00:05:17,000 --> 00:05:18,160
Let's go one-on-one.

100
00:05:18,439 --> 00:05:19,439
If I beat you today,

101
00:05:19,439 --> 00:05:20,639
you let us pass, how about that?

102
00:05:20,639 --> 00:05:22,639
No, no, no. Well, miss,

103
00:05:23,720 --> 00:05:25,720
you are a descendant of the Dian King,

104
00:05:26,319 --> 00:05:28,519
guarding his tomb for generations, right?

105
00:05:28,519 --> 00:05:30,600
Since you know my identity,

106
00:05:30,839 --> 00:05:32,160
you should know

107
00:05:32,639 --> 00:05:34,439
I will absolutely never let you in.

108
00:05:34,879 --> 00:05:36,720
If you really are a descendant of the Dian King,

109
00:05:37,160 --> 00:05:38,199
let me show you something.

110
00:06:03,319 --> 00:06:04,600
You growing this

111
00:06:05,399 --> 00:06:07,839
is also because you stole others' treasures.

112
00:06:08,040 --> 00:06:10,600
You brought this upon yourself and deserve it.

113
00:06:11,040 --> 00:06:13,399
If you insist on finding the Dian King's treasure cave,

114
00:06:13,879 --> 00:06:15,360
that would be compounding your mistakes.

115
00:06:15,600 --> 00:06:18,720
Your illness will only get worse.

116
00:06:19,160 --> 00:06:20,040
We didn't.

117
00:06:20,720 --> 00:06:23,040
He got this strange illness because he accompanied me

118
00:06:23,040 --> 00:06:24,360
to the Modi Underworld Ruins for archaeology.

119
00:06:24,920 --> 00:06:25,879
Do you have a way to cure it?

120
00:06:25,879 --> 00:06:27,199
Talking about archaeology,

121
00:06:28,839 --> 00:06:31,000
it's just trying to find a legitimate excuse

122
00:06:31,680 --> 00:06:34,680
for your own voyeuristic desires.

123
00:06:35,120 --> 00:06:35,839
Miss,

124
00:06:36,079 --> 00:06:37,240
if you put it that way,

125
00:06:37,240 --> 00:06:38,879
you're being a bit narrow-minded.

126
00:06:39,160 --> 00:06:40,800
We are doing archaeology,

127
00:06:40,839 --> 00:06:42,879
which is fundamentally different from those thieves.

128
00:06:43,040 --> 00:06:44,639
We are not destroying cultural relics.

129
00:06:45,079 --> 00:06:48,720
We are excavating and protecting civilization.

130
00:06:48,720 --> 00:06:49,240
Right, right, right.

131
00:06:49,639 --> 00:06:50,319
Miss,

132
00:06:50,639 --> 00:06:51,800
along our journey here,

133
00:06:51,800 --> 00:06:53,160
every little thing we've discovered

134
00:06:53,160 --> 00:06:54,959
represents the highly developed

135
00:06:54,959 --> 00:06:57,079
and splendid civilization of the Dian King era.

136
00:06:57,399 --> 00:06:59,040
Whether in aesthetics or technology,

137
00:06:59,040 --> 00:07:01,000
it is all something we should be proud of.

138
00:07:01,040 --> 00:07:03,439
They are monuments in the history of our national civilization.

139
00:07:03,600 --> 00:07:05,240
We excavate it

140
00:07:05,240 --> 00:07:07,040
to let the whole world see

141
00:07:07,079 --> 00:07:09,639
that we once had a beautiful civilization

142
00:07:09,639 --> 00:07:12,199
capable of arousing national self-confidence.

143
00:07:12,199 --> 00:07:13,360
Isn't that a good thing?

144
00:07:13,759 --> 00:07:15,879
I have no time to listen to your sophistry.

145
00:07:16,240 --> 00:07:17,959
Surround them.

146
00:07:53,120 --> 00:07:53,959
This won't work.

147
00:07:54,199 --> 00:07:55,600
This... it has thorns.

148
00:07:55,639 --> 00:07:56,480
Don't... don't move.

149
00:07:56,800 --> 00:07:57,639
The thorns are poisonous.

150
00:07:57,959 --> 00:07:59,279
This... this is too wicked.

151
00:07:59,360 --> 00:08:01,160
I gave you a chance.

152
00:08:01,800 --> 00:08:05,000
Now you can only die.

153
00:08:07,720 --> 00:08:10,399
Fire arrows!

154
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:13,959
They're firing arrows!

155
00:08:24,199 --> 00:08:26,079
Fatty, quickly chop off these poisonous thorns!

156
00:08:26,079 --> 00:08:26,800
Okay!

157
00:08:31,240 --> 00:08:32,399
Oh my god.

158
00:08:32,399 --> 00:08:33,799
If they use fire attacks,

159
00:08:33,799 --> 00:08:35,320
we'll become roast ducks.

160
00:08:44,600 --> 00:08:46,480
Old Lu, your mouth is really jinxed.

161
00:08:46,799 --> 00:08:48,279
Whatever bad things you say come true.

162
00:09:05,320 --> 00:09:06,679
Don't let them escape!

163
00:09:09,879 --> 00:09:11,080
Hurry, hurry, hurry!

164
00:09:20,480 --> 00:09:21,840
They haven't caught up, right?

165
00:09:22,000 --> 00:09:22,879
Not for now.

166
00:09:25,440 --> 00:09:25,960
Let's go.

167
00:09:26,279 --> 00:09:27,080
Are we still going?

168
00:09:28,000 --> 00:09:28,720
Professor Lu.

169
00:09:28,960 --> 00:09:30,080
Is there no end to this?

170
00:09:49,039 --> 00:09:50,279
This is the Heavenly Gate.

171
00:09:52,679 --> 00:09:55,039
This Heavenly Gate aligns with the path of ascension.

172
00:09:55,360 --> 00:09:56,679
The tomb of the Dian King

173
00:09:57,440 --> 00:09:59,159
is hidden right behind this Heavenly Gate.

174
00:09:59,799 --> 00:10:01,080
Even without that theory,

175
00:10:01,279 --> 00:10:02,960
isn't this the only path we have?

176
00:10:02,960 --> 00:10:05,080
You're such a know-it-all.

177
00:10:06,399 --> 00:10:07,360
I actually quite appreciate

178
00:10:07,360 --> 00:10:09,240
his courage to challenge authority.

179
00:10:09,480 --> 00:10:11,360
If you're willing to take me as your master,

180
00:10:11,360 --> 00:10:12,480
I wouldn't object.

181
00:10:12,840 --> 00:10:14,080
Stop talking nonsense.

182
00:10:14,159 --> 00:10:15,240
The kid definitely wouldn't want to.

183
00:10:15,240 --> 00:10:16,399
He's a scientist.

184
00:10:16,399 --> 00:10:17,559
What's wrong with being a scientist?

185
00:10:18,639 --> 00:10:21,080
The art of Feng Shui also needs to keep up with the times.

186
00:10:21,080 --> 00:10:22,399
Do you think I'm right?

187
00:10:23,559 --> 00:10:24,000
I say,

188
00:10:24,240 --> 00:10:25,840
we can't stay here for long.

189
00:10:25,840 --> 00:10:27,080
In case they catch up,

190
00:10:27,080 --> 00:10:28,279
we'll be doomed again.

191
00:10:29,919 --> 00:10:30,279
I'm telling you,

192
00:10:30,279 --> 00:10:31,799
your mouth is totally jinxed.

193
00:10:31,799 --> 00:10:32,759
They've caught up!

194
00:10:32,799 --> 00:10:34,440
Hurry, go, let's go!

195
00:10:34,600 --> 00:10:36,240
Hurry, hurry, let's go!

196
00:12:13,039 --> 00:12:13,840
Old Chen, watch out!

197
00:12:49,279 --> 00:12:50,080
I'm exhausted.

198
00:12:51,039 --> 00:12:51,799
Are you okay?

199
00:12:59,639 --> 00:13:00,679
If we keep fighting like this,

200
00:13:00,840 --> 00:13:03,159
we'll only drain each other and both end up hurt.

201
00:13:03,159 --> 00:13:04,159
You're older than me.

202
00:13:04,279 --> 00:13:05,840
You'll definitely die of exhaustion first.

203
00:13:06,600 --> 00:13:07,799
I once promised

204
00:13:08,559 --> 00:13:11,200
that we from Guyu wouldn't take a single thing on this trip.

205
00:13:11,559 --> 00:13:13,039
Your relentless harassment like this,

206
00:13:13,559 --> 00:13:15,279
isn't it a bit unreasonable?

207
00:13:18,200 --> 00:13:20,799
You trespassed into the forbidden grounds without permission.

208
00:13:20,960 --> 00:13:22,080
The fact that you're still alive

209
00:13:22,279 --> 00:13:24,080
is already me showing mercy.

210
00:13:26,480 --> 00:13:27,080
Wait.

211
00:13:28,600 --> 00:13:31,240
This is the ancient whistle of the Guyu bee tamers.

212
00:13:32,080 --> 00:13:34,960
Thirty years ago, they were brutally massacred by the Xieling faction.

213
00:13:35,399 --> 00:13:36,799
Could it be that you are a survivor

214
00:13:36,799 --> 00:13:38,240
of that disaster?

215
00:13:44,679 --> 00:13:45,639
Everyone, go, hurry!

216
00:13:45,679 --> 00:13:46,480
Keep up!

217
00:13:46,480 --> 00:13:47,480
Go!

218
00:13:48,799 --> 00:13:50,120
Go, go, go!

219
00:13:50,240 --> 00:13:50,799
Hurry up!

220
00:13:51,159 --> 00:13:53,639
Go, go, go!

221
00:13:54,399 --> 00:13:55,399
Don't move!

222
00:13:55,480 --> 00:13:57,480
Go, go, go!

223
00:13:58,799 --> 00:14:00,840
Speak, where is the tomb of the Dian King?

224
00:14:03,600 --> 00:14:04,480
You won't say, huh?

225
00:14:05,679 --> 00:14:06,399
You, come out!

226
00:14:06,399 --> 00:14:07,120
What are you doing?

227
00:14:08,080 --> 00:14:08,559
Go!

228
00:14:13,480 --> 00:14:14,480
Tell me,

229
00:14:16,080 --> 00:14:17,279
where is the tomb of the Dian King?

230
00:14:17,919 --> 00:14:18,720
Grandpa!

231
00:14:21,080 --> 00:14:22,600
All of my clansmen

232
00:14:23,559 --> 00:14:26,639
stay here to protect the Dian King.

233
00:14:27,480 --> 00:14:29,600
We never spare our own lives.

234
00:14:30,879 --> 00:14:32,879
It's you who have done all these

235
00:14:32,879 --> 00:14:35,399
wicked and immoral things.

236
00:14:36,279 --> 00:14:40,000
Sooner or later, you'll be struck by lightning.

237
00:14:40,000 --> 00:14:42,279
Struck by lightning? Let's see who gets struck first!

238
00:14:42,279 --> 00:14:43,000
Speak up!

239
00:14:53,799 --> 00:14:54,600
What was that?

240
00:15:03,919 --> 00:15:04,720
Grandpa!

241
00:15:04,840 --> 00:15:05,519
A-Bao!

242
00:15:10,799 --> 00:15:11,600
A-Bao!

243
00:15:11,720 --> 00:15:13,679
No matter what happens outside,

244
00:15:13,679 --> 00:15:14,919
you must not come out.

245
00:15:14,919 --> 00:15:16,159
No, Grandpa!

246
00:15:16,320 --> 00:15:17,039
A-Bao!

247
00:15:18,240 --> 00:15:20,679
You are our only hope!

248
00:15:21,080 --> 00:15:22,360
Do you hear me?
